1
00:02:15,212 --> 00:02:16,814
我 被 卡 住 了 !
I'm stuck!

2
00:02:24,020 --> 00:02:25,054
退回 去 !
Get back!

3
00:03:01,551 --> 00:03:02,785
敦 蒂 先生
Mr. Tweedy.

4
00:03:03,552 --> 00:03:06,522
那 只 雞 在 圍 欄 外 干 什 么 ?
What is that chicken doing outside the fence?

5
00:03:06,588 --> 00:03:08,523
我 不知道 親愛 的
Oh! I don't know, love

6
00:03:08,557 --> 00:03:11,326
馬上 去處 理 一下 !
Just deal with it. Now!

7
00:03:17,231 --> 00:03:21,367
讓 我 難堪 我 要 教訓 你
I'll teach you to make a fool out of me

8
00:03:23,936 --> 00:03:26,238
這 對 你們 都是 一個 教訓 !
Let that be a lesson to the lot of ya!

9
00:03:26,305 --> 00:03:30,708
沒有 雞 能 從 敦 蒂 雞 場 逃出去 !
No chicken escapes from Tweedy's farm!

10
00:06:08,140 --> 00:06:10,875
早 安 姜 妹 剛 度 完 假 ?
Morning, Ginger. Back from holiday?

11
00:06:10,975 --> 00:06:13,110
我 沒去 度 假 巴 波斯
I wasn't on holiday, Babs.

12
00:06:13,110 --> 00:06:14,278
我 被 關 禁閉 了
I was in solitary confinement

13
00:06:14,378 --> 00:06:16,113
一個人 獨 呆 一陣子 也不 錯
Oh, it's nice to get a bit of time to yourself

14
00:06:16,113 --> 00:06:16,713
是 不是 ?
isn't it?

15
00:06:20,583 --> 00:06:22,585
集合 !
Roll call!

16
00:06:22,718 --> 00:06:24,286
馬上 過來 你們 列隊 要 晚 了
Come along, now. You'll be late for parade

17
00:06:24,353 --> 00:06:26,955
嘰 嘰 嘰 嘰 快點 兒 左 右 左 右
Pip, pip. Quick march. Left, right, left, right

18
00:06:27,022 --> 00:06:28,223
左 右 左 右 !
Left, right, left, right!

19
00:06:28,256 --> 00:06:29,791
快 精神 點 兒
Come on. Smarten up.

20
00:06:29,858 --> 00:06:31,426
紀 律 ! 秩序 !
Discipline! Order!

21
00:06:31,526 --> 00:06:33,027
想 當初 在 皇家 空 軍
Back in my R. A. F. days

22
00:06:33,027 --> 00:06:34,528
當 長官 命令 緊急 起 飛
when the officer called for a scramble

23
00:06:34,595 --> 00:06:36,330
你 跳進 老 飛 機 發現 目標
you'd hop in the old crate and tally- ho.

24
00:06:36,330 --> 00:06:37,097
轟隆 開 走了 !
Chocks away!

25
00:06:37,164 --> 00:06:38,732
別說 了 老 傻瓜
Give over, you old fool.

26
00:06:38,732 --> 00:06:40,133
他們 只想 數數 我們
They just want to count us

27
00:06:40,233 --> 00:06:42,502
你 怎 么 敢 這樣 對 長官 回 話 ?
How dare you talk back to a senior ranking officer?

28
00:06:42,602 --> 00:06:44,603
嘿 想 當初 在 皇家 空 軍 ...
Why, back in my R. A. F. days!

29
00:06:44,603 --> 00:06:45,704
福 羅 他們 來了
Fowler, they're coming

30
00:06:45,771 --> 00:06:47,105
啊 好 好
Oh, right, right.

31
00:06:48,607 --> 00:06:50,241
你 要 受到 嚴厲 的 譴責
There will be a stern reprimand for you, lad.

32
00:06:50,241 --> 00:06:51,542
取消 你的 自由 活動
You're grounded

33
00:06:52,710 --> 00:06:54,412
立 正 !
Attention!

34
00:06:58,448 --> 00:07:01,684
歡迎 你 回來 母雞 有 新 的 計劃 嗎 ?
Welcome back, hen. Is there a new plan?

35
00:07:14,128 --> 00:07:16,897
我 想 我們 試 過 從 下面 出去
I thought we tried going under

36
00:07:16,997 --> 00:07:18,999
噢 上面 好
Ah! Over. Right

37
00:07:28,040 --> 00:07:29,541
雞蛋 的 數量 怎 么 樣 ?
How's the egg count?

38
00:07:29,641 --> 00:07:31,209
我 今 早 下了 五個 五個
I've laid five eggs this morning. Five!

39
00:07:31,309 --> 00:07:33,110
那 很好 我 ... 很 高興
Well- chuffed with that, I was!

40
00:07:33,177 --> 00:07:35,079
產 蛋 記錄

41
00:07:39,983 --> 00:07:43,119
啊 不 愛 德 文 娜
Oh, no. Edwina

42
00:07:44,320 --> 00:07:46,355
邦 迪 你 為 什 么 不 給 她 幾個 ?
Bunty, why didn't you give her some of yours?

43
00:07:46,455 --> 00:07:48,356
我 會 的 可 她 沒說
I would have. She didn't tell me.

44
00:07:48,356 --> 00:07:49,691
她 沒 對 任何人 說
She didn't tell anyone

45
00:07:57,164 --> 00:07:59,899
噢 愛 德 文 娜 要 去 度 假 嗎 ?
Oh, is Edwina off on holiday?

46
00:08:45,738 --> 00:08:48,840
我們 必須 逃離 此地
We've got to get out of here

47
00:08:48,907 --> 00:08:51,142
姜 妹 ! 我們 還要 逃 嗎 ?
Ginger! Are we still on?

48
00:08:51,242 --> 00:08:53,311
啊 當然 啦 我們 要 逃
Oh, we're on, all right

49
00:08:53,411 --> 00:08:56,447
麥 克 告訴 大家 今晚 在 17 號 木 屋 開會
Spread the word, Mac. Meeting tonight in hut 17

50
00:09:18,198 --> 00:09:20,033
你 叫 我們 ? 尼 克 ...
You called? Nick and...

51
00:09:20,100 --> 00:09:22,368
- 范 晨 - 聽從 你的 吩咐
- Fetcher. - At your service

52
00:09:25,704 --> 00:09:27,272
這 邊 兒 來
Over here

53
00:09:29,741 --> 00:09:31,242
我們 還 需要 一些 東西
We need some more things

54
00:09:31,342 --> 00:09:32,477
好 小 姐
Right you are, miss.

55
00:09:32,477 --> 00:09:34,345
這 套 手工 茶 具 怎 么 樣 ?
How about this quality handcrafted tea set?

56
00:09:34,412 --> 00:09:35,179
不要
Uh, no

57
00:09:35,246 --> 00:09:36,213
那 來 條 漂亮 的 項鏈 和 掛 墜 ?
Or a lovely necklace and pendant?

58
00:09:36,213 --> 00:09:36,713
是 不錯 ...
It's love...

59
00:09:36,780 --> 00:09:38,215
或者 這個 美麗 的 帽 子
Or this beautiful number

60
00:09:38,248 --> 00:09:40,283
都是 巴 黎 雞 圈 子 里 時 髦 的 東西
all the rage in the fashionable chicken coops of Paree

61
00:09:40,383 --> 00:09:42,018
這樣 戴上
Simply pop it on like so

62
00:09:42,118 --> 00:09:43,819
像 法 國 雞 那樣 說 聲 " 喔 哇 "
and as the French hens say, " Voila! "

63
00:09:43,919 --> 00:09:44,854
那是 法 語
That's French

64
00:09:44,954 --> 00:09:46,889
這 是個 兩 用 帽 小 姐
That's two hats in one, miss.

65
00:09:46,889 --> 00:09:48,623
參加 晚 會 參加 婚禮
For parties, for weddings

66
00:09:48,723 --> 00:09:51,159
啊 可是 女士 這 使 你 美 極 了
Oh, but madame, this makes you look like a vision

67
00:09:51,159 --> 00:09:51,926
像 夢中 美人
like a dream

68
00:09:52,060 --> 00:09:53,994
- 像 只 鴨 子 - 不要 謝謝
- Like a duck. - No, thank you

69
00:09:54,495 --> 00:09:56,296
我們 在 做 這個 需要 這些
We're making this. We need THESE things.

70
00:09:56,296 --> 00:09:57,130
你 能 搞 到 嗎 ?
Can you get them?

71
00:09:57,231 --> 00:10:00,200
啊 啊 這 不容 易 小 姐
Oh, oh, oh, this is a big job, miss

72
00:10:00,300 --> 00:10:01,567
啊 比 其 它 的 都 難
Oh, bigger than the others.

73
00:10:01,567 --> 00:10:02,935
不 不 價錢 會 很 貴
No, no. This is gonna cost

74
00:10:03,035 --> 00:10:05,371
價錢 不變 一袋 種子
Same as always. One bag of seed

75
00:10:05,371 --> 00:10:06,805
- 這 是 你的 付 款 ? - 是 雞 飼料
- You call this pay? - It's chicken feed

76
00:10:07,606 --> 00:10:09,107
- 我們 還能 給 你 什 么 ? - 雞蛋
- What else could we give you? - Eggs

77
00:10:09,174 --> 00:10:10,708
- 雞蛋 ? - 雞蛋
- Eggs? - Eggs

78
00:10:10,775 --> 00:10:12,510
我們 不能 給 你 雞蛋 太 珍貴 了
We can't give you eggs. They're too valuable

79
00:10:12,577 --> 00:10:13,944
我們 也 珍貴
And so are we

80
00:10:15,312 --> 00:10:16,780
你 先 請 范 晨
After you, Fetcher

81
00:10:17,914 --> 00:10:19,416
我 先 請 什 么 ?
After I what?

82
00:10:19,516 --> 00:10:20,850
走 !
Move!

83
00:10:28,890 --> 00:10:30,792
二十 二 加 九
Twenty- two and nine

84
00:10:30,859 --> 00:10:33,094
十四 先 令 加 三 便 士
Fourteen shillings and threepence

85
00:10:33,194 --> 00:10:35,829
七 加 六 便 士 乘 三
Seven and sixpence times three

86
00:10:35,896 --> 00:10:37,431
二 加 九
Two and nine

87
00:10:37,497 --> 00:10:40,100
四個 半 便 士
Fourpence ha'penny

88
00:10:40,166 --> 00:10:43,002
蠢 材 沒用 的 東西 !
D- oh! Stupid, worthless creatures!

89
00:10:43,135 --> 00:10:47,706
我 做 夠 薄 利生 意 了
I'm sick and tired of making minuscule profits

90
00:10:48,573 --> 00:10:50,475
厭倦 賺 小錢 的 生意 了

91
00:10:52,610 --> 00:10:54,912
將你 的 雞 場 變成 金 礦

92
00:11:01,384 --> 00:11:03,019
我 發財 了 !

93
00:11:03,519 --> 00:11:05,287
啊 對
Oh, yes

94
00:11:05,354 --> 00:11:07,155
這些 雞 有 什 么 詭計
Those chickens are up to something

95
00:11:07,256 --> 00:11:09,457
安靜 我 找到 了 一個 方法
Quiet. I'm onto something

96
00:11:09,557 --> 00:11:11,292
它們 組織 起來 了 我 知道
They're organized. I know it

97
00:11:11,426 --> 00:11:13,294
- 我 說 安靜 - 那個 姜 妹
- I said, quiet. - That ginger one

98
00:11:13,361 --> 00:11:14,929
我 認為 她是 頭 兒
I reckon she's their leader

99
00:11:15,029 --> 00:11:16,030
敦 蒂 先生 !
Mr. Tweedy!

100
00:11:16,797 --> 00:11:18,765
我 想 我 最終 找到 了
I may finally have found a way to

101
00:11:18,765 --> 00:11:19,733
生 財 之道
make us some real money here

102
00:11:19,799 --> 00:11:21,334
而 你 卻 在 干 什 么 ?
and what are you on about?

103
00:11:21,401 --> 00:11:22,935
愚蠢 地 在 想 雞 會 逃跑
Ridiculous notions of escaping chickens

104
00:11:23,002 --> 00:11:24,270
但是 ... 但是 ...
But... But...

105
00:11:24,336 --> 00:11:27,005
都是 你 想 象 的 敦 蒂 先生 你 說
It's all in your head, Mr. Tweedy. Say it!

106
00:11:27,105 --> 00:11:29,007
都是 我 想 象 的 都是 我 想 象 的
It's all in me head. It's all in me head

107
00:11:29,107 --> 00:11:31,676
現在 你 自己 對 自己 重 復
Now, you keep telling yourself that

108
00:11:31,743 --> 00:11:33,944
因為 我 再也 不想 聽到 它 了
because I don't want to hear another word about it

109
00:11:34,011 --> 00:11:36,580
- 清楚 了 嗎 ? - 清楚 了 親愛 的
- Is that clear? - Yes, love

110
00:11:36,680 --> 00:11:38,215
但 你 知道 那個 姜 妹 ...
But you know that ginger one...

111
00:11:38,281 --> 00:11:40,550
它 只是 只 雞 傻瓜 !
It's chickens, you dolt!

112
00:11:40,650 --> 00:11:41,551
除你 之外
Apart from you

113
00:11:41,551 --> 00:11:43,519
它們 是 地球 上 最 蠢 的 動物
they're the most stupid creatures on this planet!

114
00:11:43,619 --> 00:11:46,088
他們 不會 搞 陰謀 詭計
They don't plot, they don't scheme

115
00:11:46,088 --> 00:11:47,556
他們 沒有 組織
and they are not organized

116
00:11:48,857 --> 00:11:51,059
秩序 ! 秩序 !
Order! Order!

117
00:11:51,125 --> 00:11:54,428
大家 安靜 安定
Quiet, everyone. Settle down.

118
00:11:54,528 --> 00:11:56,096
我 請 你們 注意 秩序 ...
I would like to call to order! Please

119
00:11:56,096 --> 00:11:57,564
如果 你們 能夠 ...
if you could just...

120
00:11:57,631 --> 00:12:00,433
大家 有 點 兒 紀 律 ! 什 么 什 么 !
Let's have some discipline in the ranks! What, what!

121
00:12:00,533 --> 00:12:02,301
- 謝謝 福 羅 - 當年 我 在 皇家 空 軍
- Thank you, Fowler. - In my R. A. F. day

122
00:12:02,402 --> 00:12:03,536
我們 從不 允許
we were never allowed to waste time

123
00:12:03,536 --> 00:12:04,670
閑 聊 浪費 時間
with unnecessary chit- chat

124
00:12:04,770 --> 00:12:06,438
是 謝謝你 福 羅
Yes, thank you, Fowler

125
00:12:06,538 --> 00:12:07,839
我 ...
I...

126
00:12:09,808 --> 00:12:11,609
對 !
Right!

127
00:12:13,844 --> 00:12:15,379
繼續 吧
Carry on

128
00:12:16,914 --> 00:12:19,149
我 知道 上次 的 逃跑 行動
Now, I know our last escape attempt was

129
00:12:19,149 --> 00:12:20,183
有 點 兒 失敗
a bit of a fiasco

130
00:12:20,283 --> 00:12:22,652
但 麥 克 和 我 又有 了 新 計劃
but Mac and I have come up with a brand- new plan

131
00:12:22,752 --> 00:12:24,020
- 給 他們 看看 麥 克 - 好
- Show 'em, Mac. - Right

132
00:12:24,053 --> 00:12:26,288
我們 試 著 從 鐵 絲 網 下 出去 但 沒有 成功
We tried going under the wire and that didn't work

133
00:12:26,355 --> 00:12:29,724
因此 這個 計劃 是 ... 從 上面 過
So, the plan is... we go OVER it

134
00:12:30,725 --> 00:12:31,959
這 是 我們 明白 嗎 ?
This is us, right?

135
00:12:32,060 --> 00:12:33,828
我們 這樣 進去
We get in like this

136
00:12:33,928 --> 00:12:36,463
把 它 拉緊 ... 松 手 !
Wind her up and... let her go!

137
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:43,636
天 啊 這個 蘿 卜 完 蛋 了 !
Good grief! The turnip's bought it!

138
00:12:45,170 --> 00:12:48,040
農夫 來了 !
Farmer's coming!

139
00:12:51,209 --> 00:12:53,044
隱蔽 行動 !
Operation Cover- up!

140
00:13:14,095 --> 00:13:17,030
敦 蒂 先生 !
Mr. Tweedy!

141
00:13:17,130 --> 00:13:20,300
- 你 在 哪兒 ? - 都是 你 想 象 的
- Where are you? - Ooh. It's all in your head

142
00:13:20,400 --> 00:13:22,101
都是 你 想 象 的 都是 你 想 象 的
It's all in your head. It's all in your head

143
00:13:24,770 --> 00:13:27,472
各位 想想 我們 還有 什 么 沒有 試 過 ?
Think, everyone, think. What haven't we tried yet?

144
00:13:29,174 --> 00:13:31,042
我們 還沒 試 過 不 逃跑
We haven't tried NOT trying to escape

145
00:13:31,142 --> 00:13:32,643
嗯 那 可能 行 得 通
Hmm. That might work

146
00:13:32,743 --> 00:13:34,845
記得 愛 德 文 娜 ?
What about Edwina?

147
00:13:34,912 --> 00:13:37,948
還 得 有 多少 空 窩 才 行 ?
How many more empty nests will it take?

148
00:13:38,048 --> 00:13:39,516
也許 如果 她 花 更多 的 時間 下蛋
Perhaps it wouldn't be empty

149
00:13:39,582 --> 00:13:40,717
而不是 逃跑
if she'd spent more time laying

150
00:13:40,717 --> 00:13:42,085
她 的 窩 就 不會 空
and less time escaping

151
00:13:42,185 --> 00:13:43,753
所以 你 一生 都 在 下蛋 ...
So laying eggs all your life...

152
00:13:43,819 --> 00:13:45,087
然 后 被 拔 毛 填 料 烘 烤
and then getting plucked, stuffed

153
00:13:45,087 --> 00:13:45,754
這樣 夠 好了 吧 ?
and roasted is good enough?

154
00:13:45,821 --> 00:13:47,589
這 是 命運
It's a living

155
00:13:47,656 --> 00:13:49,824
你們 知道 問題 在 哪兒 嗎 ?
You know what the problem is?

156
00:13:49,924 --> 00:13:51,826
圍 欄 不僅僅 將 農場 圍住
The fences aren't just round the farm.

157
00:13:51,826 --> 00:13:53,561
也 將你 們 的 思想 圍住 了
They're up here in your heads

158
00:13:53,661 --> 00:13:55,596
那 里 有 個 更好 的 地方
There's a better place out there

159
00:13:55,596 --> 00:13:56,964
就 在 山丘 那邊 兒
somewhere beyond that hill

160
00:13:57,064 --> 00:14:00,967
那 里 空間 開闊 樹木 眾多 ...
and it has wide open spaces and lots of trees...

161
00:14:01,067 --> 00:14:02,635
還有 草原
and grass

162
00:14:02,702 --> 00:14:06,438
你 能 想 象 出 嗎 ? 翠綠 的 草原
Can you imagine that? Cool, green grass

163
00:14:06,505 --> 00:14:09,241
- 誰 來 喂 我們 ? - 我們 自 力 更 生
- Who feeds us? - We feed ourselves

164
00:14:09,307 --> 00:14:11,009
- 那 農場 在 哪兒 ? - 沒有 農場
- Well, where's the farm? - There is no farm

165
00:14:11,109 --> 00:14:12,510
那 農夫 住 在 哪兒
Then where does the farmer live?

166
00:14:12,510 --> 00:14:13,944
沒有 農夫 巴 波斯
There is no farmer, Babs

167
00:14:14,045 --> 00:14:16,013
- 他 去 度 假 了 嗎 ? - 他 哪兒 也沒 去
- Is he on holiday? - He isn't anywhere

168
00:14:16,046 --> 00:14:17,281
你 還不 明白 嗎 ?
Don't you get it?

169
00:14:17,381 --> 00:14:18,982
沒有 早 點名 沒有 農夫
There's no morning head count, no farmers

170
00:14:18,982 --> 00:14:20,316
沒有 狗 雞 舍 和 鑰匙
no dogs, coops and keys

171
00:14:20,417 --> 00:14:22,819
也沒有 圍 欄
and no fences

172
00:14:22,952 --> 00:14:26,822
我 一生 中 從沒 有 聽過 如此 精 彩 的 ...
In all my life I've never heard such a fantastic...

173
00:14:26,922 --> 00:14:28,223
一堆 廢話 !
load of tripe!

174
00:14:29,491 --> 00:14:31,192
哎 面對 現實 吧 親愛 的
Oh, face the facts, ducks

175
00:14:31,292 --> 00:14:32,860
從 這 兒出 去 的 機 率
The chances of us getting out of here

176
00:14:32,860 --> 00:14:34,095
只有 百 萬分 之一
are a million to one

177
00:14:34,995 --> 00:14:36,930
那 我們 仍有 機會
Then there's still a chance

178
00:14:54,445 --> 00:14:57,314
啊 不 啊 不 我 在 干 什 么 ?
Oh, no, oh, no, oh, no. What am I doing?

179
00:14:57,414 --> 00:14:58,615
你 想 騙 誰 ?
Who are you trying to fool?

180
00:14:58,615 --> 00:15:00,984
你 不能 誘騙 這 群 ...
You can't lead this bunch of...

181
00:15:02,552 --> 00:15:04,353
啊 老 天 幫幫 我們
Oh, heaven help us

182
00:15:12,226 --> 00:15:14,695
自由 !
Freedoooom!

183
00:15:29,374 --> 00:15:30,909
女士 們 先生 們 謝謝你 們
Thank you, ladies and gentlemen

184
00:15:30,942 --> 00:15:32,610
你們 是 極 好 的 觀 眾
You've been a wonderful audience

185
00:15:33,177 --> 00:15:35,779
噢 好 的
Oh, yes

186
00:15:46,722 --> 00:15:48,323
有 辦法 了 !
That's it!

187
00:15:48,423 --> 00:15:49,724
快 把 他 搬進 去
Get him inside quickly

188
00:15:55,663 --> 00:15:57,564
這 是 我們 出去 的 辦法
THIS is our way out of here

189
00:15:57,664 --> 00:15:59,065
我們 做 海 報 ?
We'll make posters?

190
00:15:59,165 --> 00:16:01,968
不 是 海 報 上 的 畫 兒 巴 波斯
No. What's ON the poster, Babs. What's ON the poster

191
00:16:02,035 --> 00:16:03,269
我們 將 飛 出去 !
We'll fly out!

192
00:16:03,402 --> 00:16:05,504
有 他的 照片 一定 是個 人物
He must be important to have his picture taken.

193
00:16:05,504 --> 00:16:06,572
他 是 干 什 么 的 ?
What does he do?

194
00:16:06,705 --> 00:16:09,107
這 還不 明顯 嗎 ? 他 是 職業 飛行 公 雞
Isn't it obvious? He's a professional flying rooster

195
00:16:09,241 --> 00:16:11,142
他 在 農場 間 做 示 范 飛行
He flies from farm to farm, giving demonstrations

196
00:16:11,209 --> 00:16:13,311
- 你 這樣 認為 ? - 啊 當然
- Do you suppose? - Oh, absolutely

197
00:16:13,377 --> 00:16:15,179
不能 在 暗處 不 不能 在 這 兒
Not in the dark, no. No, not in there. No

198
00:16:15,246 --> 00:16:17,314
出去 好 要 拿 ...
Get out. Good. Gotta get...

199
00:16:21,284 --> 00:16:23,686
你們 是 誰 ? 我 在 哪兒 ? 發生 了 什 么 事 ?
Who are you? Where am I? What's going on?

200
00:16:23,753 --> 00:16:25,654
哎呀 ! 我 的 翅膀 怎 么 了 ?
Ouch! What happened to my wing?

201
00:16:25,721 --> 00:16:27,256
你 剛才 跌 得很 慘
You took a rather nasty fall

202
00:16:27,322 --> 00:16:28,790
你 扭傷 了 前 腱
And sprained the anterior tendon

203
00:16:28,857 --> 00:16:30,859
我 給 你 捏 了 捏 包 扎 了 一下 兒
I gave it a wee bit of a tweak and wrapped her up

204
00:16:30,959 --> 00:16:31,926
這 是 英 語 嗎 ?
Was that English?

205
00:16:31,926 --> 00:16:33,427
你 扭傷 了 翅膀 她 弄 好了
You sprained a wing. She fixed it

206
00:16:33,561 --> 00:16:36,563
- 是 我 做 的 繃帶 - 是 我 抱 你 進來 的
- I made the bandage. - I- I carried you in

207
00:16:40,066 --> 00:16:42,368
我們 從頭 開始 說 我 在 哪兒 ?
Let's back up and start from the top. Where am I?

208
00:16:42,435 --> 00:16:44,804
你 說得 對 真 沒 禮 貌 我們 只是 太 激動 了 ...
You're right. How rude. We're just very excit...

209
00:16:44,870 --> 00:16:46,405
這 是個 養 雞 場
This is a chicken farm

210
00:16:46,472 --> 00:16:48,073
我們 都是 雞
And we're the chickens

211
00:16:48,173 --> 00:16:50,308
哦 現在 明白 了 雞 場 雞 ...
Yeah, with you so far. Chicken farm, chickens...

212
00:16:50,408 --> 00:16:51,843
我 不喜歡 他的 樣子
I don't like the look of this one.

213
00:16:51,843 --> 00:16:53,311
他 兩眼 的 距離 太近 了
His eyes are too close together

214
00:16:53,377 --> 00:16:55,579
- 福 羅 別 這樣 - 他 還 是個 美國 佬 !
- Fowler, please. - And he's a Yank!

215
00:16:55,646 --> 00:16:57,648
別 急 老大 爺 在 我們 那 兒 斗 雞 是 違法 的
Easy, Pops. Cockfighting's illegal where I come from

216
00:16:57,748 --> 00:16:59,282
那 究竟是 什 么 地方 ? ?
And where is that exactly?

217
00:16:59,349 --> 00:17:00,817
一個 我 稱之為 自由 之地
A place I call the land of the free

218
00:17:00,817 --> 00:17:01,718
勇敢 之 家 的 地方
and the home of the brave

219
00:17:01,818 --> 00:17:04,186
- 蘇 格 蘭 ! - 不 美國
- Scotland! - No! America

220
00:17:04,320 --> 00:17:06,288
美國
Oh! America

221
00:17:06,388 --> 00:17:08,924
胡 扯 愛 管 閑 事 的 美國 人
Poppycock. Pushy Americans.

222
00:17:08,924 --> 00:17:10,658
每次 打仗 總是 晚 出 場
Showing up late for every war

223
00:17:10,725 --> 00:17:14,328
掙 得 多 愛 得 多 來 這 兒 了 !
Overpaid, oversexed and over here!

224
00:17:14,428 --> 00:17:15,829
老 爺 爺 怎 么 啦 ?
What's eating Grandpa?

225
00:17:15,896 --> 00:17:17,864
哦 別 在 意 這 位 先生 ...
Oh, don't mind him, Mister! Mister?

226
00:17:17,931 --> 00:17:20,834
我 叫 洛 基 · 羅德 紅 島 的 洛 基 簡 稱 羅德
Name's Rocky. Rocky the Rhode Island Red. Rhodes for short

227
00:17:20,934 --> 00:17:23,803
- 洛 基 · 羅德 ? - 很 順 耳 是 吧 ?
- Rocky Rhodes? - Catchy, ain't it?

228
00:17:23,903 --> 00:17:26,238
羅德 先生 這 是 你 嗎 ?
Um, Mr. Rhodes, is this you?

229
00:17:27,172 --> 00:17:29,274
誰 想 知道 ?
Uh, who wants to know?

230
00:17:29,374 --> 00:17:31,109
一 群 十分 絕望 的 雞
A group of rather desperate chickens

231
00:17:31,175 --> 00:17:32,510
你 看 如果 是 你
You see, if it is you

232
00:17:32,577 --> 00:17:35,279
那 你 可能 就是 我們 祈禱 的 答案
then you just might be the answer to our prayers

233
00:17:37,080 --> 00:17:40,783
那 么 就 叫 我 奇 跡 吧 娃 娃 臉 因為 那 就是 我
Well, then, call me a miracle, dollface, 'cause that's me

234
00:17:41,984 --> 00:17:44,086
你 怎 么 來 英 國 了 羅德 先生 ?
And what brings you to England, Mr. Rhodes?

235
00:17:44,153 --> 00:17:46,822
那 當然是 因為 英 國 的 美 女 了
Why, all the beautiful English chicks, of course

236
00:17:46,922 --> 00:17:49,324
別 逗 了 !
Give over!

237
00:17:49,424 --> 00:17:51,292
你 看 我 天生 喜歡 旅行
You see, I'm a traveler by nature

238
00:17:51,392 --> 00:17:53,127
我 在 農 舍 呆 過
I've done the whole barnyard thing

239
00:17:53,127 --> 00:17:54,628
但 我 很不 適 應
but I couldn't get into it

240
00:17:54,728 --> 00:17:57,130
嗨 你 好 ? 諾 鋪
Hi. How are you? Nope

241
00:17:57,231 --> 00:17:58,832
自由 自 在 這 才是 我 的 方式
The open road. That's more my style

242
00:17:58,932 --> 00:18:01,201
對 給 我 個 背 包
Yep, just give me a pack on my back

243
00:18:01,201 --> 00:18:02,335
告訴 我 方向
and point me where the wind blows

244
00:18:02,402 --> 00:18:04,770
實際上 你 知道 在 我 家鄉 他們 叫 我 什 么 嗎 ?
In fact, you know what they call me back home?

245
00:18:04,870 --> 00:18:07,973
你們 會 喜歡 的 孤獨 的 自由 浪 人
You're gonna love this. The Lone Free Ranger

246
00:18:08,073 --> 00:18:10,308
很 偉大 吧 ?
Isn't that great?

247
00:18:10,408 --> 00:18:12,410
- 我 知道 有 可能 - 有 可能 對
- I knew it was possible. - Oh, it's possible, all right

248
00:18:12,477 --> 00:18:14,011
- 我 知道 會有 辦法 的 - 阿們 !
- I knew the answer would come. - Amen!

249
00:18:14,078 --> 00:18:15,746
我們 都 將 飛過 那個 圍 欄
We're all going to fly over that fence

250
00:18:15,813 --> 00:18:17,881
羅德 先生 給 我們 示 范 對 吧 ?
and Mr. Rhodes is going to show us how, right?

251
00:18:18,015 --> 00:18:21,417
那 ... 什 么 ? 你 說 " 飛 " ?
That's... What? Did you say " fly" ?

252
00:18:21,484 --> 00:18:23,786
- 你 可以 教 我們 - 不 我 不能
- You can teach us. - No, I can't

253
00:18:23,853 --> 00:18:25,321
聽 著 噓 你們 聽到 了 嗎 ?
Listen. Shh. You hear that?

254
00:18:26,655 --> 00:18:28,557
那是 自由 大道 在 叫 我
That's the open road calling my name

255
00:18:28,557 --> 00:18:30,291
我 生來 就 對 此 有 反應
and I was born to answer that call

256
00:18:30,625 --> 00:18:32,760
他的 聽 力 一定 很好
He must have very good hearing

257
00:18:33,394 --> 00:18:36,330
是 是 出口 在 哪兒 ? 啊 在 這 兒
Okay, okay, where's the exit? Ah, this way

258
00:18:36,430 --> 00:18:37,698
羅德 先生 也許
Mr. Rhodes, um, perhaps

259
00:18:37,698 --> 00:18:39,733
我 沒有 把 我們 的 處境 講 清楚
I didn't explain our situation properly

260
00:18:39,833 --> 00:18:41,734
我們 一天 到 晚 下蛋
We lay eggs day in and day out

261
00:18:41,801 --> 00:18:43,736
當 我們 再也 不能 下蛋 時 他們 就 殺了 我們
and when we can't lay any more, they kill us

262
00:18:43,836 --> 00:18:45,971
這 是個 殘酷 的 世界 娃 娃 臉
It's a cruel world, doll face.

263
00:18:45,971 --> 00:18:47,206
你 或許 應該 適 應 它
You might as well get used to it

264
00:18:47,306 --> 00:18:49,941
" 他們 要 殺 我們 " 你 都 明白 了 嗎 ?
Which part of " they kill us" do you not understand?

265
00:18:50,008 --> 00:18:51,643
我 也有 自己 煩惱 的 事
I got my own set of problems to worry about

266
00:18:51,709 --> 00:18:53,477
此外 從 這個 鳥 籠 子 出去 也 并 不太 難
Besides, this birdcage can't be that hard to bust out of

267
00:18:53,577 --> 00:18:55,512
實際上 瞧 著 我
In fact, watch me

268
00:18:55,579 --> 00:18:57,781
一 只 甚至 兩 只 雞
It's not so hard to get one chicken

269
00:18:57,781 --> 00:18:59,149
出去 并 不 難
out of here or even two

270
00:18:59,216 --> 00:19:01,217
但 我們 全 要 出去
but this is about all of us

271
00:19:01,317 --> 00:19:02,852
全部 出去 ?
All of you?

272
00:19:02,885 --> 00:19:04,320
這 就是 我 一直 想 告訴 你的
That's what I've been trying to tell you

273
00:19:04,353 --> 00:19:05,888
等等 讓 我 搞 清楚
Wait a minute. Let me get this straight

274
00:19:05,988 --> 00:19:07,422
你 想 讓 所有 的 雞
You want to get every chicken

275
00:19:07,422 --> 00:19:08,857
同時 從 這 兒 逃出 ?
in this place out of here at the SAME TIME?

276
00:19:08,957 --> 00:19:11,592
- 當然 - 你 瘋了 !
- Of course. - You're certifiable!

277
00:19:11,726 --> 00:19:13,127
你 不能 做 這 種 驚 險 的 事
You can't pull off a stunt like that.

278
00:19:13,127 --> 00:19:13,661
這 是 自殺
That's suicide

279
00:19:13,728 --> 00:19:14,929
有 志 者 事 竟 成
Where there's a will, there's a way

280
00:19:14,962 --> 00:19:17,798
完全 同意 我 要 從 那 兒 走了
Couldn't agree more. I WILL be leaving that way

281
00:19:17,864 --> 00:19:19,432
- 但 ... 請 別 走 ! - 我 就是 這 種 人 ...
- But... Please! - I'm the type of guy

282
00:19:19,466 --> 00:19:23,069
我 喜歡 自由 我 從來 沒有 在 一個 地方 ...
That likes to roam around I'm never in one...

283
00:19:38,181 --> 00:19:40,550
原來 如此 你 是 馬 戲 團 的
So that's it. You're from the circus

284
00:19:42,018 --> 00:19:43,452
你 是 逃出來 的 是 不是 ?
You're on the run, aren't you?

285
00:19:43,819 --> 00:19:45,421
你 能不能 小聲 點 兒 ?
You wanna keep it down?

286
00:19:45,487 --> 00:19:47,489
我 正在 躲藏
I'm trying to lay low here.

287
00:19:47,556 --> 00:19:49,958
我 應當 馬上 宣揚 出去
I should turn you in right now

288
00:19:50,058 --> 00:19:51,726
你 不會 的 對 吧 ?
You wouldn't. Would you?

289
00:19:51,726 --> 00:19:53,094
給 我 個 不會 的 理由
Give me one reason why I shouldn't

290
00:19:53,160 --> 00:19:54,862
因為 我 很 ... 可愛 ?
Because I'm... cute?

291
00:19:58,131 --> 00:20:00,366
嗨 嗨 ! 你 是 哪種 瘋 雞 ?
Hey, hey, hey! What kind of crazy chick are you?

292
00:20:00,467 --> 00:20:02,268
你 知道 我 被 找到 下 場會 咋 樣 ?
Do you know what'll happen if he finds me?

293
00:20:02,335 --> 00:20:02,969
這 是個 殘酷 的 世界
It's a cruel world

294
00:20:03,102 --> 00:20:04,603
我 剛剛 決定 我 不喜歡 你
I just decided. I don't like you

295
00:20:04,703 --> 00:20:05,704
我 剛剛 決定 我 不 在 乎
I just decided. I don't care.

296
00:20:05,704 --> 00:20:06,805
現在 給 我們 示 范 飛行
Now, show us how to fly

297
00:20:06,905 --> 00:20:08,974
- 用 這 只 翅膀 ? - 那 就 教 我們 吧
- With this wing? - Teach us, then

298
00:20:09,107 --> 00:20:10,175
不 !
No!

299
00:20:11,276 --> 00:20:13,177
他 很有 價值 你 剛才 說 ?
He's valuable, you say?

300
00:20:13,244 --> 00:20:14,945
- 當然 - 拿 電 筒 來
- Sure. - Get the torch

301
00:20:15,045 --> 00:20:16,213
現在 聽 著 姊妹
Now, you listen here, sister.

302
00:20:16,213 --> 00:20:17,681
我 再也 不想 過 那 種 生活 了
I'm not going back to that life

303
00:20:17,748 --> 00:20:19,883
我 是個 孤獨 的 自由 浪 人 喜歡 自由
I'm a Lone Free Ranger. Emphasis on FREE!

304
00:20:19,983 --> 00:20:22,218
那 也是 我們 的 追求 自由 !
And that's what we want. Freedom!

305
00:20:25,721 --> 00:20:26,989
喜歡 自由 他們 向 這 里 走來 了
Fancy that. They're coming this way

306
00:20:27,089 --> 00:20:28,924
啊 不 他們 是 來 抓 我 的
Oh, oh, no. No. They're on to me

307
00:20:29,024 --> 00:20:30,658
教 我們 飛行 我們 就 把 你 藏起來
Teach us to fly and we'll hide you

308
00:20:30,758 --> 00:20:31,959
如果 我 不 呢 ?
And if I don't?

309
00:20:32,994 --> 00:20:35,062
你 爸爸 也是 這 么 卑鄙 嗎 ?
Was your father by any chance a vulture?

310
00:20:35,162 --> 00:20:36,697
我們 成 交了 嗎 ?
Do we have a deal?

311
00:20:52,376 --> 00:20:53,911
是 實行 交易 的 時候 了 娃 娃 ...
Time to make good on that deal, doll...

312
00:20:53,978 --> 00:20:56,246
我 叫 姜 妹
The name is Ginger

313
00:21:09,758 --> 00:21:11,726
- 舒服 嗎 ? - 不太 舒服
- Comfortable? - Not really

314
00:21:11,826 --> 00:21:13,594
這 也許會 有 所 幫助
Maybe this will help

315
00:21:13,661 --> 00:21:15,763
藏 窩 不錯
Nice hideout

316
00:21:15,863 --> 00:21:17,664
哎 喲 比 蛋 殼 還 小
Ouch. I had more room in my egg

317
00:21:17,731 --> 00:21:19,299
我們 履行 了 我們 的 諾言
We've held up our end of the deal.

318
00:21:19,299 --> 00:21:20,567
明天 你 得 履行 你的 了
Tomorrow you hold up yours

319
00:21:20,633 --> 00:21:22,168
- 什 么 諾言 ? - 飛行 !
- What deal? - The flying!

320
00:21:22,235 --> 00:21:23,869
噢 對 對 別 擔心
Yeah, yeah, yeah. Right, right, right. Don't worry

321
00:21:23,969 --> 00:21:25,537
我 將 傾 囊 相 授
I'll teach you everything I know

322
00:21:25,638 --> 00:21:27,973
現在 我 的 床 在 哪兒 ?
Now, which bunk is mine?

323
00:21:30,275 --> 00:21:32,944
真是 太 氣 人 了 !
Absolutely outrageous!

324
00:21:33,044 --> 00:21:35,346
讓 一個 長官 和 別人 睡 一張 床 ...
Asking a senior officer to share his quarters...

325
00:21:35,446 --> 00:21:37,681
和 一個 美國 小 兵 太過 分 了
and with a noncommissioned Yank, no less

326
00:21:37,781 --> 00:21:39,616
想 當初 我 從 ...
Why, back in my day, I'd never!

327
00:21:39,716 --> 00:21:42,452
你 也不 是 我 的 首 選
You weren't exactly my first choice, either

328
00:21:42,518 --> 00:21:44,386
挪開 點 兒 你的 翅膀 到 我 這 邊 兒 了
And scoot over. Your wing's on my side of the bunk

329
00:21:44,487 --> 00:21:45,921
你 那邊 兒 ?
Your side of the bunk?

330
00:21:45,988 --> 00:21:48,056
整 張床 都是 我 的
The WHOLE bunk is my side of the bunk!

331
00:21:48,123 --> 00:21:51,793
等等 ... 什 么 味道 ? 是 你的 口 臭 ?
Just... What's that smell? Is that your breath?

332
00:21:51,893 --> 00:21:54,195
真是 太 氣 人 了 !
It's absolutely outrageous

333
00:21:58,798 --> 00:22:01,534
因此 你們 想 飛行 嗯 ?
So you wanna fly, huh?

334
00:22:01,634 --> 00:22:03,169
好 這 并 不容 易
Well, it ain't gonna be easy

335
00:22:03,169 --> 00:22:04,703
一 朝 一 夕 是 學 不會 的
and it ain't gonna happen overnight

336
00:22:04,770 --> 00:22:06,338
你 知道 飛行 得 有 三樣 東西
You see, flying takes three things

337
00:22:06,438 --> 00:22:09,641
努力 練 習 不 屈 不 撓 ...
Hard work, perseverance and...

338
00:22:09,741 --> 00:22:12,176
- 努力 練 習 - 你 說 兩次 努力 練 習 了 !
- Hard work. - You said hard work twice!

339
00:22:12,276 --> 00:22:13,444
那是 因為
That's because

340
00:22:13,444 --> 00:22:16,080
它 比 不 屈 不 撓 難 兩倍
it takes twice as much work as perseverance

341
00:22:16,146 --> 00:22:18,949
一派胡言 !
Codswallop!

342
00:22:20,250 --> 00:22:22,685
現在 最 重要 的 是
Now, the most important thing is

343
00:22:22,685 --> 00:22:24,386
我們 要 共同 合作
we have to work as a team

344
00:22:24,487 --> 00:22:26,955
這 意味 著 ... 我 說什 么 你們 就 做什 么
which means... you do everything I tell you

345
00:22:29,324 --> 00:22:32,360
好 ! 我們 開始 吧 !
Right! Let's rock and roll!

346
00:23:03,152 --> 00:23:07,022
敦 蒂 先生 ! 雞 都 在 ...
Mrs. Tweedy! The chickens are...

347
00:23:07,089 --> 00:23:09,157
吃食 ?
Pecking?

348
00:23:09,224 --> 00:23:13,027
左 二 三 右 二 三
And left, two, three. And right, two, three

349
00:23:13,160 --> 00:23:16,430
嗯 ... 停下 啊 對 往 下
And... stop right there. Oh, yeah, down

350
00:23:16,497 --> 00:23:19,366
往 下 對 轉 小 圈 就 這樣 快點 兒
Down. Yeah, make little circles. That's it. Faster

351
00:23:19,432 --> 00:23:23,469
快點 兒 對 好極了
Faster. Oh, yes. Perfect

352
00:23:23,536 --> 00:23:26,738
噢 就是 這 兒
Oh, that's the spot.

353
00:23:34,011 --> 00:23:36,380
我 以為 你 要 教 我們 飛 呢
I thought you were going to teach us how to fly

354
00:23:36,480 --> 00:23:38,448
我 正在 教 啊
That's what I'm doing

355
00:23:38,548 --> 00:23:40,917
不是 該 有 些 拍 翅膀 的 動 作 嗎 ?
Isn't there usually some flapping involved?

356
00:23:41,050 --> 00:23:43,686
嘿 我 告訴 你 怎 么 下蛋 了 嗎 ?
Hey, do I tell YOU how to lay eggs?

357
00:23:43,753 --> 00:23:45,721
放心 我們 正在 進步
Relax. We're making progress

358
00:23:45,788 --> 00:23:50,025
真的 ? 我 總 覺得 我們 在 兜 圈 子
Really? I can't help feeling we're going around in circles

359
00:23:50,091 --> 00:23:53,294
這 ... 嘿 ! 停下 ! 你們 讓 我 頭 暈
What the... Hey! Cut it out! You're making me dizzy

360
00:23:53,394 --> 00:23:55,496
我 想 他們 準備 好 飛行 了
I think they're ready to fly now

361
00:23:55,562 --> 00:23:57,164
好 因為 他們 再也 走 不動 了
Good, because they certainly can't walk anymore

362
00:23:59,633 --> 00:24:01,801
過來 姑娘 我們 拍 翅膀
Up and at 'em, gals. Let's flap

363
00:24:05,738 --> 00:24:06,939
瞧 范 晨
Watch, Fetcher

364
00:24:07,005 --> 00:24:09,274
我們 看看 老 母雞 是否 改變 了 主意
Let's see if old Attila the Hen has come to her senses

365
00:24:14,845 --> 00:24:16,513
下 起 雞 雨 了 !
It's raining hen!

366
00:24:20,617 --> 00:24:22,618
- 這 是 什 么 把 戲 親愛 的 ? - 我們 在 飛
- What's this caper, love? - We're flying

367
00:24:22,718 --> 00:24:24,220
當然
Obviously

368
00:24:24,320 --> 00:24:27,155
拍 翅膀 看 這 兒 范 晨
Flipping hell. Look at this, Fetch

369
00:24:27,222 --> 00:24:28,957
他們 找 死 啊
They're gonna kill themselves

370
00:24:29,024 --> 00:24:31,292
- 想看 下去 ? - 想 看 吧
- Wanna watch? - Yeah, all right

371
00:24:40,100 --> 00:24:42,802
嗨 ! 小心 那些 雞蛋 !
Hey! Careful of those eggs!

372
00:24:45,938 --> 00:24:48,206
單 煎 一面
Sunny- side up.

373
00:24:49,941 --> 00:24:51,809
現在 他們 很 容易 翻過 來 !
Now they're over easy!

374
00:24:53,211 --> 00:24:54,678
無疑 成了 炒 蛋
Definitely scrambled

375
00:24:56,246 --> 00:24:57,781
走 ! 走 ! 走 !
Go! Go! Go!

376
00:24:57,881 --> 00:25:00,083
走 走 走 !
Go, go, go, go! Go!

377
00:25:00,183 --> 00:25:02,218
雞 在 行動 !
Poultry in motion!

378
00:25:13,527 --> 00:25:15,296
物 以 類 聚 人以 群 分
Birds of a feather flop together

379
00:25:20,033 --> 00:25:21,567
干 得 好 女士 們 干 得 好 !
Great work, ladies. Great work!

380
00:25:21,634 --> 00:25:24,336
受 點 兒 苦 對 你們 不錯 是好 事
The pain you're feeling is a good thing. It's good

381
00:25:24,437 --> 00:25:26,005
痛苦 是 你們 的 朋友 對 吧 ? 這 是好 事
Pain is your friend, okay? It's a positive thing

382
00:25:26,071 --> 00:25:27,739
堅定 信念 ... 你 叫什 么 名字 ?
Just keep the faith, uh... What's your name?

383
00:25:27,739 --> 00:25:28,840
安 吉 絲 ! 你 會 成功 的
Agnes! You'll get there

384
00:25:28,974 --> 00:25:30,508
小 鴨 我 想你 今天 飛過 四 英 尺 了 !
Ducky, I think you flew four feet today!

385
00:25:30,575 --> 00:25:33,911
對 四 英 尺 ! 從 屋頂 到 地面
Right, four feet! From the roof to the ground

386
00:25:34,011 --> 00:25:35,079
女士 們 別 擔心
It's all part of the process, ladies.

387
00:25:35,079 --> 00:25:36,113
這 是 成功 的 必 由 之路
Nothing to worry about!

388
00:25:36,213 --> 00:25:37,781
你 這個 吃奶 酪 的 小 ...
Ya cheese- eating little...

389
00:25:40,250 --> 00:25:42,452
這 聽起來 不太 好
That doesn't sound good. Ha, ha, ha

390
00:25:42,518 --> 00:25:44,653
聽 大地 在 震動 我們 需要 擔心 嗎 ?
Okay, the ground's shaking. Are we worried?

391
00:25:44,753 --> 00:25:46,622
我們 需要 擔心 嗎 ?
Are we worried?

392
00:25:51,759 --> 00:25:54,261
馬 戲 團 快 把 我 藏起來
The circus. Quick. Hide me

393
00:25:54,361 --> 00:25:55,963
- 藏起來 - 來
- Hide me. - Come on

394
00:25:56,063 --> 00:25:58,465
像 瘋 雞 一樣 亂 拍 翅膀
One isn't awarded a medal

395
00:25:58,465 --> 00:26:00,100
是 得 不 到 獎 章 的
like this for flapping about like a lunatic

396
00:26:00,200 --> 00:26:02,768
你 看 這 兒 這 是 長官 的 地方
Now, see here! This is an officer's quarters

397
00:26:02,835 --> 00:26:03,769
快 到 這 兒 來
Quick. In here.

398
00:26:03,769 --> 00:26:04,770
馬上 出去 先生 !
Get out of here immediately, sir!

399
00:26:04,837 --> 00:26:06,605
夠了 老 爺 爺
Give it a rest, Pops

400
00:26:06,672 --> 00:26:09,708
出去 ! 本 周 我 不會 饒 了 你
Out of here! I shall have you on a charge within the week

401
00:26:12,844 --> 00:26:14,478
家禽 產 品 有 限 公 司

402
00:26:40,300 --> 00:26:41,901
謝謝 伙 計
Cheers, mate

403
00:26:47,005 --> 00:26:49,274
都是 你 想 象 的 都是 你 想 象 的
It's all in your head. It's all in your head

404
00:26:49,341 --> 00:26:50,942
都是 你 想 象 的
It's all in your head

405
00:26:56,280 --> 00:26:58,849
什 么 ... 什 么 ... 這些 是 什 么 ?
What... What... What's all this, then?

406
00:26:58,949 --> 00:27:00,750
這 是 我們 的 未來 敦 蒂 先生
This is our future, Mr. Tweedy

407
00:27:00,817 --> 00:27:02,518
再也 不用 浪費 時間
No more wasting time with petty

408
00:27:02,518 --> 00:27:04,220
收集 雞蛋 和 算 小 賬 了
egg collection and minuscule profits

409
00:27:04,286 --> 00:27:07,489
不 收集 蛋 了 ? 可 我們 一直是 雞 農
No more eggs? But we've always been egg farmers

410
00:27:07,556 --> 00:27:09,024
我 父親 的 父親 的 父親
Me father and his father and all their fathers.

411
00:27:09,024 --> 00:27:10,058
他們 都是 ...
They was always...

412
00:27:10,158 --> 00:27:13,160
窮 光 蛋 ! 一 文 不值
Poor! Worthless. Nothings

413
00:27:13,261 --> 00:27:14,762
但 這 一切 都要 改變 了
But all that's about to change

414
00:27:14,862 --> 00:27:17,531
這 將使 敦 蒂 雞 場 走出 黑暗 的 年代 ...
This will take Tweedy's farm out of the dark ages...

415
00:27:17,631 --> 00:27:20,567
進入 大規模 的 自動 化 生產
and into full- scale automated production

416
00:27:21,834 --> 00:27:24,570
我 再也 不是 窮 光 蛋 了
Melisha Tweedy will be poor no longer

417
00:27:25,471 --> 00:27:26,839
操作 指 南

418
00:27:26,872 --> 00:27:29,307
那 我 把 它 安裝 起來 好嗎 ?
I'll put it together, then, shall I?

419
00:27:34,011 --> 00:27:35,613
這 不太 妙 麥 克
This isn't good, Mac

420
00:27:35,713 --> 00:27:37,848
盒 子 里 的 東西 是 給 我們 的
Whatever's in those boxes is for us

421
00:27:37,881 --> 00:27:38,949
我 想 不是 軟 草
and I don't think it's softer hay

422
00:27:39,049 --> 00:27:41,050
啊 母雞 我 討厭 說 喪 氣 話
Aye, hen. And I hate to be the voice of doom

423
00:27:41,117 --> 00:27:42,685
但 我 一直 在 思考
but I've been calculating

424
00:27:42,685 --> 00:27:44,620
我們 生來 就 不適合 飛行
and I just don't think we're built for flying

425
00:27:44,720 --> 00:27:47,589
但 我 看到 他 飛過 鐵 絲 網
But I saw him. He flew in over that fence

426
00:27:47,689 --> 00:27:49,491
啊 啊 我 相信 你
Aye, aye, I believe you

427
00:27:49,491 --> 00:27:51,125
但 如果 我們 能 親眼 看看
but if we could just see it for ourselves

428
00:27:51,192 --> 00:27:52,760
那 就 能說 明 問題 了
that may answer some questions

429
00:27:52,827 --> 00:27:54,628
你 說得 對 對不起
You're right. I'm sorry

430
00:27:54,695 --> 00:27:56,630
我們 練 了 一個 周 可 一點 兒進 展 都 沒有
We've been at this all week, and we're getting nowhere

431
00:27:56,697 --> 00:27:59,366
如果 他的 翅膀 好 點 兒 他 就 ...
If his wing were better, he could!

432
00:27:59,366 --> 00:28:00,967
啊 ! 我 去 跟 他 說說
Oh! I'll have a word with him

433
00:28:05,771 --> 00:28:07,105
他 在 哪兒 ?
Where is he?

434
00:28:07,206 --> 00:28:10,308
他們 給 我 獎 章 不是 因為 我 是 美國 保姆
They didn't give me this medal for being a Yank nanny

435
00:28:10,375 --> 00:28:12,210
一句 簡單 的 " 我 不知道 " 就 足夠 了
A simple " I don't know" would suffice

436
00:28:12,310 --> 00:28:15,346
當心 那位 小 姜 妹
Beware of that one, young Ginger

437
00:28:15,412 --> 00:28:17,381
那個 美國 佬 不可 信任
That Yank is not to be trusted

438
00:28:17,481 --> 00:28:20,617
他 是 我們 離開 這 兒 的 希望
That YANK is our ticket out of here

439
00:28:21,251 --> 00:28:21,884
豬 對馬 說
And the pig says to the horse

440
00:28:21,884 --> 00:28:24,086
" 嗨 伙 計 為 什 么 臉 拉 這 么 長 ? "
" Hey, fella, why the long face? "

441
00:28:25,621 --> 00:28:27,989
噢 瞧 瞧
Oh, oh, look, look

442
00:28:28,090 --> 00:28:30,692
啊 雞 尾 酒 !
Oh. Cocktail!

443
00:28:30,825 --> 00:28:31,993
別 逗 了 !
Give over!

444
00:28:36,563 --> 00:28:39,332
好吧 ... 無論如何 ...
So, um, anyway...

445
00:28:39,432 --> 00:28:41,668
明天 要 記住 飛行 事項
Remember those flying tips tomorrow.

446
00:28:41,668 --> 00:28:42,568
這 很 重要
They're very important

447
00:28:42,635 --> 00:28:44,937
一直 保持 想 飛 的 念頭
Keep thinking those flighty thoughts

448
00:28:45,004 --> 00:28:46,805
噢 好
Oh, yeah

449
00:28:46,872 --> 00:28:48,407
他們 是 一流 的 雞 真的 是
They're swell chicks. They really are

450
00:28:48,473 --> 00:28:50,041
瞧 巴 波斯 給 我 織 了 什 么
Look at what Babs made me

451
00:28:50,108 --> 00:28:52,410
一個 口 罩 很 可愛 吧 ?
A beak warmer. Isn't that the cutest?

452
00:28:52,510 --> 00:28:55,446
那個 邦 迪 她 真有 勁
And that Bunty. She really packs a punch

453
00:28:55,546 --> 00:28:57,447
有 什 么 問題 嗎 ?
Is there a problem here?

454
00:28:57,581 --> 00:28:59,182
- 我們 飛過 圍 欄 了 嗎 ? - 還沒有
- Have we flown over that fence? - Not quite

455
00:28:59,316 --> 00:29:00,483
那 就 有 問題 了
Then there's a problem

456
00:29:00,550 --> 00:29:01,951
耐心 等待 才能 成功 娃 娃 臉
Good things come to those who wait, dollface

457
00:29:02,018 --> 00:29:03,552
姜 妹 !
Ginger!

458
00:29:10,492 --> 00:29:12,493
- 好 你 花了 多 長時間 ? - 做什 么 ?
- Okay, how long did it take you? - To do what?

459
00:29:12,593 --> 00:29:14,128
學習 飛行 啊
To learn how to fly

460
00:29:14,195 --> 00:29:15,362
蘋果 和 橘 子 洋 娃 娃
Apples and oranges, baby doll.

461
00:29:15,362 --> 00:29:16,497
我 有 天賦 他們 卻 沒有
I'm gifted. They're not

462
00:29:16,563 --> 00:29:18,665
兩者 不能 比較 對 吧 ?
You can't compare the two, okay?

463
00:29:18,732 --> 00:29:20,400
問題 是 這些 事情 要 花 時間
The point is, these things take time

464
00:29:20,500 --> 00:29:21,701
而 我們 很快 就 沒有 時間 了
Which we are rapidly running out of

465
00:29:21,768 --> 00:29:23,769
我們 甚至 還沒 離開 地面
We haven't even lifted off the ground. Why?

466
00:29:23,869 --> 00:29:25,471
信心 我 反復 想過
Trust. I went over my calculations

467
00:29:25,571 --> 00:29:27,472
我 認為 關鍵 的 因 素 是 信心
and I figured the key element was trust

468
00:29:30,141 --> 00:29:31,709
我 一點 兒 也不 明白
I- I didn't get a word of that

469
00:29:31,809 --> 00:29:33,477
當 鴨 子 和 鵝 飛行 時
When birds like ducks and geese take off

470
00:29:33,477 --> 00:29:35,346
他們 有 什 么 呢 ? 信心 !
what do they have? Trust!

471
00:29:35,412 --> 00:29:37,648
我 發誓 她 用 錯了 詞
I swear she ain't using real words

472
00:29:37,714 --> 00:29:40,083
- 她 說 我們 需要 更多 的 動 力 - 哦 動 力
- She said we need more thrust. - Oh, thrust

473
00:29:40,150 --> 00:29:42,151
當然 我們 需要 動 力
Well, of course, we need thrust.

474
00:29:42,151 --> 00:29:44,320
動 力 和 飛行 像 ... 這個 !
Thrust and flying are like... this!

475
00:29:44,420 --> 00:29:47,456
- 希望 你 不 介意 ? - 當然
- Would you excuse us? - Aye

476
00:29:47,522 --> 00:29:49,357
啊 翅膀 翅膀 翅膀
Ah, the wing, the wing, the wing

477
00:29:49,491 --> 00:29:51,559
如果 明天 我們 還 看 不 到 結果 交易 就 取消 了
If we don't see some results by tomorrow, the deal is off

478
00:29:51,659 --> 00:29:53,661
沒有 掩 護 了 他們 會 找到 你
No more hiding. They will find you

479
00:29:53,661 --> 00:29:55,396
你 回 馬 戲 團 去 吧 飛 人 !
and it's back to the circus, flyboy!

480
00:29:55,462 --> 00:29:59,666
我 從沒 遇到 像 你 這樣 難 交 的 雞
You're the first chick I ever met with the shell still on

481
00:29:59,733 --> 00:30:02,368
睡 個 好 覺 天使 臉
Sleep tight, angel face. The Rock's on the case

482
00:30:09,107 --> 00:30:13,477
喔 ... 喔 ! 什 么 什 么
Cock- a- doodle- doo! What, what

483
00:30:14,512 --> 00:30:17,180
啊 很 漂亮 朋友
Oh, it was a beaut, guv'nor

484
00:30:17,281 --> 00:30:19,649
如果 讓 我 說 一件 藝 術 精 品
A fine piece of work, if I do say so meself

485
